data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bed, 2.5 bath brick ranch in the well-established neighborhood of Fairfield. The inviting front porch is perfect for enjoying quiet mornings with a cup of coffee, and the open layout is perfect for gatherings & entertaining. You'll find gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the main living areas. The family room is complete with a gas fireplace & opens up to the eat-in kitchen area. This kitchen is perfect for the culinary enthusiast- equipped with stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, granite counters, & ample cabinet space. Off the kitchen you’ll find a FROG, laundry room & powder room. You will love the primary suite complete with two walk-in closets & a large glass shower. Step outside to the back deck, an ideal setting for outdoor dining under the lights. Additional features include a walk-in attic, sprinkler system, raised garden beds, a utility sink in the laundry room, & oversized garage with workbench. Schedule your tour today!
